extendedInfo.description: Rabobank's Mobile Banking App gives you secure account access from your mobile device anytime, anywhere using your existing Rabobank Online Banking Username and Password. You can sign in with your secure online banking credentials, knowing your information is protected by encryption technology. You can make deposits, manage your accounts, find ATMs and more. You'll enjoy a fast, optimized experience from your mobile device. Your security is our priority - Mobile data transmissions are safeguarded by 128-bit SSL (Secure Socket Layer) to prevent unauthorized access. Our Online Security Guarantee provides added protection against unauthorized access to your accounts. We will never transmit your account number, and we will not store your username or password on your phone. MOBILE DEPOSIT * Deposit checks using your smartphone MONITOR YOUR ACCOUNT * See account balances & transaction history for all of your accounts BILL PAY * Schedule payments and pay bills right from your mobile device * If you're already a Bill Pay customer, your payees are automatically available for use in the mobile app. TRANSFERS * Make transfers between your Rabobank accounts. FIND LOCATIONS AND CONTACT RABOBANK * Map the nearest Rabobank branches & ATMs. * Contact a service representative for assistance. 1. Rabobank's Mobile App is subject to the carrier's message and data rates. Use of this application is subject to your carrier's message and data rates. 2. Mobile Deposits are subject to verification and may not be available for immediate withdrawal. A statement should also be added referring the user to the terms and conditions.3. Bill Pay services that customers must be approved/enrolled in the appropriate program first. You can then add a reference directing the user to the terms and conditions of the online banking agreement. * Minimum system requirements:* Android phones with an operating system version 2.2 and above. Not compatible with Android tablets. These will be supported in the near future.Rabobank, N.A. Member FDIC Copyright Rabobank, N.A. 2013

reviews.title: Remote Deposit
reviews.comment: I love the fact that I don\'t have to go to a branch to deposit a check, I just don\'t like that it take 24 to 48 hours to show up on your account, it feels like my check is lost in cyber world. Would be nice of it showed at least pending.
reviews.author: Mario A Garcia Jr

reviews.title: Remote Deposit!
reviews.comment: Easy to use, great interface, love the ability to deposit checks remotely.  The camera zooms automatically when you snap the picture of your check...    Will definitely be using this app regularly.
reviews.author: Chris Thomas

reviews.title: Great app!
reviews.comment: Remote Deposit is easy to use.  It was great seeing my deposit in my account without ever going to the bank.
reviews.author: Jeff Hall

reviews.title: Business accounts NOT allowed
reviews.comment: The app I\'ve been waiting for for years finally arrives, and I cannot login. I call customer service and they said that business accounts are not allowed.Furthermore, they are not aware of plans to allow business account access in the future. Inexcusable!
reviews.author: Gene Hrubi

reviews.title: At long last
reviews.comment: What a sad sad sad day when you have waited so long only to be disappointed. The camera to use for check deposit needs to be worked on because it has no focus and cropping ability. Please fix.

reviews.title: Totally frustrated!

You would think that Rabobank would be trying to make their business banking customers happier, not making things harder and harder for them! Get with the game Rabobank!

reviews.title: Good, but needs color coding
reviews.comment: Just installed, and it seems pretty good so far, but I wish it had some kind of easier way to distinguish between withdrawals and deposits so you can spot them easier. Maybe color coding, or at least a plus or minus sign next to the amount number. I want to be able to scan for deposits easily instead of searching for the word \"Dep\" on the left hand side.
